text: Inverness Caledonian Thistle Football Club is a professional football club based at Caledonian Stadium in Inverness, Scotland. They play in the Scottish Championship and are currently managed by Billy Dodds. == Current squad == ===International players === Six players have represented their country whilst contracted to Caley Thistle.
